We're excited to announce that **Hades II** is now being tracked on CRC!

## Categories Available

- Underworld Any%
- Surface Any%
- Chaos Trials (all 15 trials)
- VoR4 variants

## Challenge Types

- Deathless
- Hitless
- No-Hit

## Submit Your Runs

If you've completed a challenge run in Hades II, head over to the game page and submit your run with video proof.

Good luck, and may the gods be with you!
